title: What time is SpaceX Crew-11's medical evacuation from the ISS on Jan. 14?
description: The four astronauts of SpaceX's Crew-11 mission will leave the International Space Station on Jan. 14, in the first-ever medical evacuation from the orbital lab. Here are the details.
